    public class StrongOkHttpClientBuilder
extends info.guardianproject.netcipher.client.StrongBuilderBase<StrongOkHttpClientBuilder,okhttp3.OkHttpClient>
    Creates an OkHttpClient using NetCipher configuration. Use build() if you have no other OkHttpClient configuration that you need to perform. Or, use applyTo() to augment an existing OkHttpClient.Builder with NetCipher.
